data.description: Finally, Your Once In A Lifetime Chance To Your Own Custom Built Ranch Home On Over 2 Acres Of Private Land, With No HOA Fees Or Rules! Bring Your Boat/ RV And Park It Under The Massive Covered RV Storage! Upon Entry Into This Quiet & Conveniently Located 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom Home You Will Immediately Notice In The Fireside Family Room With Indestructible Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring. The Eat-In-Kitchen With Island Breakfast Bar And Huge Outside Deck Make It Perfect For Entertaining. Spacious Laundry/ Mud Room With Garage Access Has Space For A Full Size Freezer. This Home Offers Many Storage Options, With Several Closets & Custom Crawl Space That Extends To Each Side Of Home & An Automatic 2 Car Garage. A Brand New Roof. Dog Run/ Chicken Coop Stays.
